description:
Marina is a water Pokémon trainer and has a fondness for water Pokémon over any other type.
Whilst traveling around the Orange Islands she and her Tentacruel rescued Misty`s Psyduck from drowning in the sea. After realising Misty was a water Pokémon trainer who also shared a fondness for water Pokémon they became fast friends although they had a Pokémon battle to determine who the best water Pokémon trainer is.
name: Tsubaki
